novelist leo tolstoy was a close family friend , as pasternak recalled , " my father illustrated his books , went to see him , revered him , and ... the whole house was imbued with his spirit."pasternak ( 1959 ) p 25   in a 1956 essay , pasternak recalled his father 's feverish work creating illustrations for tolstoy 's novel resurrection .

